## Comparison with JavaScript Implementation

This Python implementation fixes several critical issues in the existing JavaScript MCP:

| Feature | JavaScript MCP | Python MCP |
|---------|---------------|------------|
| Signing | ‚ùå Incorrect signatureChainId | ‚úÖ Correct (official SDK) |
| L1 Actions | ‚ö†Ô∏è Mostly works | ‚úÖ Fully working |
| User-signed Actions | ‚ùå Broken | ‚úÖ Working |
| Agent Mode | ‚ùå Not supported | ‚úÖ Supported |
| Error Messages | ‚ö†Ô∏è Generic | ‚úÖ Detailed |
| Wallet Check | ‚ùå None | ‚úÖ Verified on startup |
| TWAP Orders | ‚ùå Not implemented | ‚ö†Ô∏è Coming soon |

